%% 3.2.8 View Active Packages — sequence
%% GET /api/Package/Active
%% BR36: Only active packages appear in the catalog

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Guardian as Guardian
    participant App as Mobile App
    participant PC as PackageController
    participant PS as PackageService
    participant Repo as IRepository Package
    participant DB as SQL Server

    Guardian->>App: Open Services / Buy Package
    App->>PC: GET /api/Package/Active?keyword&page&pageSize
    PC->>PS: GetActivePackagesAsync
    PS->>Repo: Filter active status
    Repo->>DB: SELECT
    PS-->>PC: paged packages
    PC-->>App: 200 OK — cards: price, duration, thumbnail
